Ivana Miličević https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ivana_Mili%C4%8Devi%C4%87 0 Ivana Miličević (Croatian pronunciation: [ǐʋana milǐːt͡ʃevit͡ɕ]; born April 26, 1974) is an American actress and model. She is best known for playing Anastasia Rabitov/Carrie Hopewell in the Cinemax original series Banshee.
